\b 4. Problem Statement & Identification\b0\par
1. Absence of government price benchmarks in purchase context.\par
2. Lack of structured, evidence-backed complaint escalation.\par
3. Disconnected supply tiers causing opacity and stockouts.\par
4. Limited tools for transparent inventory and order status.\par
5. No unified trust + transparency mechanism.\par
\par
\b 5. Objectives\b0\par
- To enable transparent, fair pricing and order lifecycle visibility.\par
- To streamline complaint lodging and resolution tracking.\par
- To integrate wholesaler–retailer–customer interactions ethically.\par
